，佢前幾日竟然無啦啦問我阿媽，黎緊過冬返唔返去食飯，我阿媽一口say no，然後佢黑面黑足全日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a30d1e09bed0d6bd92f15cbaffa5f25d321166c","tid":22862,"uid":1044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:34:10.000Z","msg":"我老豆老母本身都係個啲大中華膠、日日幫大陸打飛機屌鳩香港點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，啲大陸親戚一嚟，佢兩個就係咁講，已經忍緊佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲支那蝗亂入我房攪鳩我啲野，佢就話細個唔識野由佢，成6歲7歲都唔識野？佢老豆老母無教？<br />\n<br />\n個時我仲係幾好脾氣，淨係話佢兩句就算，唔想嘈到隔離左右。宜家我個人都已經幾火爆吓，再攪鳩我啲野就真係同佢開片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f72a7b51bb6055fd4c7dc85fd25b91211aadf93","tid":22862,"uid":1044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:37:14.000Z","msg":"仲有個大陸舅父同表哥，個表哥都幾大隻，成18x，一真諗緊有咩位可以入，同埋夠唔夠佢揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35fdd095abb6562825a3411fd1f7d27fb81c1af","tid":22862,"uid":26873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名"},{"pid":"b437dabf64595b98782ae849b4d3c16493b23976","tid":22862,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有個大陸舅父同表哥，個表哥都幾大隻，成18x，一真諗緊有咩位可以入，同埋夠唔夠佢揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打試下入佢中路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}